name: Helix Egg Jump - Level 50 Challenge
description:
Helix Egg Jump - Level 50 Challenge is Game of Challenges and addiction
Helix Egg Jump is One of the most addictive game of helix maze game category . Unlock all monsters by reaching #Level50. You will love the game as it is a kind of addiction, where you have to save the egg and unlock all monsters. All you need to do is rotate the helix maze and let the egg or monster passed on next helix on same color.

Features
-20 Characters and 4 monsters to unlock
- 5 Backgrounds
- Interactive Game Play and UI UX
- All Bugs Fixed
- Addictive Game
